OL,3,CWorking in understaffed NHS is leaving
OL,4,Cnurses sick and 'broken', leaders warn
OL,6,FWorking in an understaffed NHS is
OL,7,Fleaving nurses sick and "broken",
OL,8,Faccording to the Royal College of
OL,9,FNursing (RCN).
OL,11,FA poll for the union and professional
OL,12,Fbody found workforce shortages are
OL,13,Fcausing nightmares and panic attacks,
OL,14,Fwhile nurses feel forced to keep
OL,15,Fworking when they are ill.
OL,17,FOfficial NHS figures for June ` the
OL,18,Fmost recent available ` show the
OL,19,Foverall sickness absence rate for NHS
OL,20,Fstaff in England was 4.9%, around one
OL,21,Fin 20 members of staff.
