OL,3,CWorking in understaffed NHS is leaving
OL,4,Cnurses sick and 'broken', leaders warn
OL,6,FAmong nurses and health visitors, the
OL,7,Ffigure was 5.3%, while it was 5.7%
OL,8,Famong midwives and 5.4% among
OL,9,Fambulance workers.
OL,11,FOverall, 29% of full-time equivalent
OL,12,Fdays that were lost to sickness among
OL,13,FNHS staff in June were due to anxiety
OL,14,Fand/or stress, including 28% among
OL,15,Fnurses.
OL,17,FThe RCN said it was receiving dozens
OL,18,Fof calls every week to its advice line
OL,19,Ffrom staff suffering burnout and
OL,20,Fneeding help for short-staffed wards.
