OL,3,CWorking in understaffed NHS is leaving
OL,4,Cnurses sick and 'broken', leaders warn
OL,6,FA survey of more than 20,000 UK
OL,7,Fnursing staff for the RCN found two
OL,8,Fthirds (66%) admitted to working while
OL,9,Fill multiple times a year, up from
OL,10,Ffewer than half (49%) in 2017.
OL,12,FStress was the biggest cause of
OL,13,Fillness given by staff (65.1%), up
OL,14,Ffrom 50% in 2017.
OL,16,FThe RCN said its analysis showed that
OL,17,Fthe numbers reporting working while
OL,18,Fsick and citing stress as the leading
OL,19,Fcause were both at an eight-year high.
