OL,3,CWorking in understaffed NHS is leaving
OL,4,Cnurses sick and 'broken', leaders warn
OL,6,FThere are currently more than 25,000
OL,7,Fnursing vacancies across the UK in the
OL,8,FNHS alone, the RCN said.
OL,10,FRCN general secretary, Professor
OL,11,FNicola Ranger, said: "Nursing staff
OL,12,Fare being driven to ill health from
OL,13,Fworking in understaffed and under-
OL,14,Fresourced services.
OL,16,F"And what's worse, many feel they
OL,17,Fcannot take time off for fear of
OL,18,Fleaving their colleagues at the mercy
OL,19,Fof brutal pressures. This simply isn't
OL,20,Fsustainable.
