OL,3,CWorking in understaffed NHS is leaving
OL,4,Cnurses sick and 'broken', leaders warn
OL,6,F"Nursing staff strive to do their best
OL,7,Ffor every patient on every shift, but
OL,8,Fthey are left with the impossible task
OL,9,Fof caring for dozens and sometimes
OL,10,Fover a hundred at a time.
OL,12,F"This is hugely detrimental to patient
OL,13,Foutcomes, but there also needs to be
OL,14,Faction to address the devastating
OL,15,Fimpact on staff themselves. The
OL,16,Freality is they're not breaking; many
OL,17,Fare already broken.
