OL,3,CWorking in understaffed NHS is leaving
OL,4,Cnurses sick and 'broken', leaders warn
OL,6,F"These findings are yet more cold,
OL,7,Fhard evidence that there are simply
OL,8,Ftoo few nursing staff to meet growing
OL,9,Fdemand.
OL,11,F"New and urgent investment is
OL,12,Fdesperately needed to grow the nursing
OL,13,Fworkforce, ensuring staff are able to
OL,14,Fwork in a safe environment and that
OL,15,Fpatients get the best care.
OL,17,F"This must be accompanied by the
OL,18,Fintroduction of safety-critical nurse-
OL,19,Fpatient ratios in all health and care
OL,20,Fsettings."
