OL,3,CWorking in understaffed NHS is leaving
OL,4,Cnurses sick and 'broken', leaders warn
OL,6,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We hugely value
OL,8,Fthe work of talented nurses, and
OL,9,Fthrough our 10-year health plan we are
OL,10,Ftaking action to improve conditions
OL,11,Ffor the overworked and demoralised
OL,12,Fworkforce we inherited.
OL,14,F"That includes rolling out high-
OL,15,Fquality occupational health support,
OL,16,Fintroducing new staff standards to
OL,17,Fmake sure flexible working is more
OL,18,Fwidely available, and cracking down on
OL,19,Fviolence, racism, and sexual
OL,20,Fharassment in the workplace.
